media:group.media:description:

Be sure to follow the editors if you like what you see.

-------------------------- Preface ---------------------------
Characters depicted in my videos are taken out of their original source context to tell new stories that reference either their source material or/and other media. These characters are given new names, are called 'actors' and are the mouth pieces for my anthology based series: Boundary Bridge.
